{"root":{"data":{"text":"导航总调度\nnavigation.launch\n输入map:地图名"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"robot.launch - 底层硬件组","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"controller.launch - 底盘主控板驱动","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"odom_publisher.launch - 里程计发布","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"odom_publisher_node - 里程计发布节点","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"里面最重要有一个误差修正系数 - 只需在：calibrate_params.yaml调整即可","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"发布odom_raw话题，，告诉 Nav2 导航算法“我以为我现在在这里”。","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"这里是创建了一个线程，0.02s计算一次位姿，最后通过odom_raw发布出去","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"发布odom_raw话题","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"订阅 cmd_vel 话题，将抽象的速度指令翻译成具体的电机转速。","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"发布话题：create_publisher(MotorsState, 'ros_robot_controller/set_motor', 1)","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"接收：x，y，z","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"发布：具体的每个轮子的转速","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"发布ros_robot_controller/set_motor话题","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"订阅：create_subscription(Pose2D, 'set_odom', self.set_odom, 1) - 坐标重置接口（set_odom）","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"输入：x，y，theta","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"动作：清零累加位移+强制速度回零","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"输出：通过set_pose话题发布当前位姿","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"发布set_pose话题","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"创建服务：create_service(Trigger, 'controller/load_calibrate_param', self.load_calibrate_param) - 供外部调用以重新加载修正系数参数","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"创建服务：create_service(Trigger, '~/init_finish', self.get_node_state) - 供外部调用以检查节点是否启动完成","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"robot_description.launch - 机器人模型","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dholpm660b40","created":1775735533064,"text":"joint_state_publisher_node","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dholprwjtt40","created":1775735545544,"text":"joint_state_publisher_gui_node","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dholpwsb44o0","created":1775735556171,"text":"robot_state_publisher_node","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"ros_robot_controller.launch - 电机控制驱动","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"imu_filter.launch - IMU滤波器","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"负责处理加速度计和陀螺仪的数据，滤除噪声","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"ekf_filter_node - EKF 滤波节点 - 传入参数ekf.yaml","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"depth_camera.launch - 深度相机","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"joystick_control.launch - 遥控手柄","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"init_pose.launch - 初始姿态估计","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"lidar.launch - 雷达类型选择","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"sllidar_a1.launch - 选择A1雷达","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"该文件负责配置串口，波特率等硬件参数，并启动雷达旋转","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"节点：sllidar_node - 最底层C++写的代码，无需深究 - 这是思岚官方提供的驱动。","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"节点：laser_filter_node - 传入参数：lidar_filters_config_a1.yaml","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"负责雷达的数据过滤 - 也是最底层C++代码 - 这是一个极度通用的库，专门用于处理雷达点云。它已经涵盖了 99% 的常见过滤功能（比如切除某个角度范围、过滤噪点、获取中值等）。","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"lidar_filters_config_a1.yaml","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"角度过滤器：只看前方+92到-92的视角","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"lower_angle: -1.6\n单位弧度","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"upper_angle: 1.6\n单位弧度","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"距离过滤器：只看中间的距离","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"lower_threshold: 0.2  最小阈值：低于 20cm 的数据扔掉","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"upper_threshold: 12.0 # 最大阈值：高于 12 米的数据扔掉","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"bringup.launch - 导航与算法启动组","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"text":"localization.launch - 负责确定自己在地图的位置\n传入参数nav2_params.yaml\n后面三个节点均由此参数文件控制","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomdopw5vk0","created":1775737419351,"text":"隔离组件容器 (nav2_container)：\n动作：LoadComposableNodes\n优势：共享内存，通信零延迟，降低 CPU 负担。\n这三个节点均受nav2_params.yaml控制","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomf4keky00","created":1775737532211,"text":"节点：map_server (地图读入)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomk6wrshs0","created":1775737929134,"text":"底层C++代码","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhomf77obxs0","created":1775737537972,"text":"节点amcl (点云定位)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomkdzvmq00","created":1775737944559,"text":"底层C++代码","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhomfdnch7k0","created":1775737551980,"text":"节点：lifecycle_manager (顺序激活)","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomkexiifs0","created":1775737946593,"text":"底层C++代码","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"navigation_base.launch - 负责路径规划和运动控制","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomplzspdk0","created":1775738353789,"text":"声明动作\n共包含8个节点\n其中只有司机部planner_server受nav2_controller_dwb.yaml参数控制\n其余七个节点均受nav2_params.yaml控制","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomspv9fgo0","created":1775738597314,"text":"节点：planner_server (规划部)\n责：负责全局路线。比如你要从起点去 3 米外的目标点，它负责在地图上画出一条避开墙壁的“绿色虚线”。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomswya22o0","created":1775738612734,"text":"节点：controller_server (司机)：\n职责：负责握着转向盘。它盯着规划部的线，算出现在轮子该转多快","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomvprfwxk0","created":1775738832176,"text":"单独的参数文件nav2_controller_dwb.yaml","layout_right_offset":{"x":617.0000066308385,"y":130.00000139709738},"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhomt3brzj40","created":1775738626611,"text":"节点：smoother_server (线路美容师)：\n职责：把“规划部”画出的生硬折线变得圆润，防止机器人走位像折线图。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomty2cb880","created":1775738693521,"text":"节点：behavior_server (抢险队)：\n职责：当机器人撞墙或被困住时，负责执行“原地旋转”、“后退”等紧急恢复动作。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomuit9n8o0","created":1775738738685,"text":"节点：bt_navigator (大项目总监)：\n职责：它拿着一份“行为树 (Behavior Tree)”。它决定了：“先定位，再规划，如果走不动了就叫抢险队”。整个导航的逻辑顺序由它定。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomuq6dji00","created":1775738754715,"text":"节点：waypoint_follower (物流快递员)：\n职责：当你一次性点了 5 个目标点时，它负责按顺序一个一个带你去。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomux8cyco0","created":1775738770072,"text":"节点：velocity_smoother (速度平滑器)：\n职责：防止机器人猛起猛停。它会把跳跃的速度指令变成平缓的加减速。","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhomv4pfhuo0","created":1775738786342,"text":"节点：lifecycle_manager (总调度/管家)：\n职责：按照 1-7 的顺序给这些部门一个个“打电话”，确认大家都睡醒了（Active）可以干活了。","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhomvzvdjsg0","created":1775738854182,"text":"剩余七个节点的参数文件：nav2_params.yaml","layout_right_offset":{"x":462.00000496506846,"y":-200.00000214938052},"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}